description: This is the kind of match that a great wrestler can use to practice new holds and new techniques, to better the winner's skills and to better this site with new moves on the mat. It is a time for the great to become greater. This is the kind of match where a new girl gets invaluable experience from a master--experiencing expert holds first hand, seeing how they work, and hopefully becoming a better wrestler for it. This is the kind of match where you get to see a girl totally dominated on the mat--fingered and made to submit. It's also the kind of match where the winner takes our biggest dildo and ass fucks the loser until she can't remember her name. In other words, this is the good kind of match!
title: Crimson Ninja (15-2)
